<title>Buyukdir Rabbimiz W5 ҲС6</title>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.G
 Buyukdir Rabbimiz
.                 C           Am  D
 Buyukdir osmonda U; madhlar boʻlsin!
.G
 Buyukdir Rabbimiz,
.                C   D  C     E
 Buyukdir Sening isming ulugʻdir!

[C1]
.   Am Em D     G      Bm       C
   Iso Masih, oxirigacha Egamizdir!
.  Am Em    D    G          Bm  C   G
   Butun osmon ulugʻ ismingdan sevinar,
.  Am     C      Am         C      G C G
   Buyukdir Rabbimiz, buyukdir osmonda U!</lyrics>
